Cyber Claw:











Cyber Claw sheeked as she saw the firepower come streaming at her. She 
leaped to the side, and spotted the attack, Nemeis Enforecer. A bot she 
never saw before. She snarled and disgused her voice, "Cease firing you 
fool!" She snarled, twitching her tail. Even though she was itching for it, 
she couldn't transform to her robot mode.
